NoteHub,is,a,free,anonymous,pastebin,designed,specifically,to,provide,one,off,publishing,for,Markdown,pages,Users,can,specify,a,font,and,color,scheme,for,each,page,Pages,come,with,their,own,short,URLs,and,basic,statistics,on,metrics,such,as,views,Developers,can,integrate,NoteHub,s,functions,into,their,own,program,or,application,using,the,REST,API,provided